# 🌐 Custom Website

This is a fully responsive and lightweight custom website built using **HTML, CSS, and optional JavaScript**. It is ideal for showcasing a portfolio, business, or personal brand. Designed with clean code, mobile optimization, and ease of customization in mind.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

/index.html → Main website page
/style.css → All website styling(N/A)
/script.js → (Optional) JavaScript interactions
/assets/ → Images, icons, and fonts(Can add in future)



---

## ✅ Features

- 💻 Fully responsive layout (mobile/tablet/desktop)
- 🌐 Built with plain HTML/CSS — no frameworks needed
- ⚡ Fast loading and optimized for performance
- 🔍 SEO-friendly structure (semantic tags, metadata)
- 🖼️ Easy image and text replacement
- 📦 Hosted via GitHub or any static site host (Netlify, Vercel, etc.)

---

